co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.lib.cube

Interface Cube

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, BatchWritable<Object,CubeFact>, Closeable, Dataset

    @Beta
public interface Cube
extends Dataset, BatchWritable<Object,CubeFact>
    Cube data set.

    Basic operations include adding CubeFacts and querying data.
